is an american actress , known for her roles as bridget hennessy in the abc sitcom 8 simple rules ( 2002–2005 ) , billie jenkins in the final season of the supernatural drama series charmed ( 2005–2006 ) , and penny in the cbs comedy series the big bang theory ( 2007–present ) for which she won a satellite award in 2012 , a critics ' choice television award in 2013 , and a people 's choice award in 2014 .

